name: Neonbeat Artstyle LoRA
description:
This is not my work and I don't plan to update or support this model. I am simply redistributing it for preservation's sake.

Many of the gens were made using the old LoRa extension and therefore don't display the LoRa in the prompt. Strengths used vary between 0.8 and 1.

Based on Neonbeat's style
